stable.changelog:
- (NEW) Added support for webp, webm, heic, heif, avif format
- (NEW) Convert format to jpeg when saved by built-in editor
- (NEW) Keeps the screen on in full image view
- (FIX) Video restart wen use prev and skip button in webm format
- (FIX) Camera folder don't pin by default in ANX camera mods
- (INT) Added heif, heic in clear cache filter and clear cache on exit
- (INT) Various internal changes, fixes and code cleaning
- (INT) Update translations
